{
  "stem": "10181.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of them had gone to France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One particular one, who I didn't know, of course-- I found out, many years later, about him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He became a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He-- he had gone east.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had just finished studying to be a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he went-- he finished up in Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, some German Jews finished up in Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was amongst those, and he, now, lives in California.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I do know that the orphanage children were treated terribly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This is-- again, I-- I don't really remember it that well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- I remembered some very vaguely, but this was explained to me many years later when I visited a town, that they took them-- they took the younger kids and put them on the rack-- you know these rack wagons, like where you put straw on-- and-- and put them on that and make the bigger kids pull the wagon through the streets.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then, they were-- the-- the-- the community was standing there watching and while they-- while they were spit at and beaten up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this-- this was done several times-- make them go through the main street and let everybody spit on them and then, sort of tried to abuse them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This is what happened to the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- it's-- it's-- there's a written record of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, the head of the orphanage, Rothschild, had left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had gone to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know exactly when.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think in the beginning of '38, and he left somebody else in charge who had been there, a-- a gentleman called Yitzhak Hirsch, who was a-- who was a journalist.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was also educator, also was a journalist.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
